note over browser:
Browser executes the event handler for submitting
the form which creates a new note out of user input.
The note is added to the end of the 'notes' list and
the browser renders said list on the display.
The code that browser executed also sends
the new note as POST-request to the server.
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa

note over server:
server adds the new note received
through POST to the data.json file
end note
